column5: Has anyone got a fishing report for Gullrock lake?
We're going to Gullrock on the 11th.Appreciate any report given.Thanks

We.ve had a early ice out this year big fish aren't all stacked as in past years because spawn has been over for a long time, but guys are catching alot of fish.As far as last week I'd give it a 8 out 10 but on Gullrock that still 100 fish aday. Water temp is 57 degrees at my docks.
Thanks, I will be at Gullrock 11-18 June...can't wait to get there!
